4 September 2019 Minister in the Presidency, Jackson Mthembu will tomorrow, 05 September 2019, brief media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held on Wednesday, the 4th of September 2019. Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Thursday, 5 September 2019Time: 10h00Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town NB: There will be a video link to GCIS Ronnie Mamoepa Media Centre, 1035 Tshedimosetso House, Frances Baard Street, Hatfield Follow the conversation on @GovernmentZA @GCISMedia #PostCabinet Enquiries:Phumla WilliamsGCIS Acting Director-GeneralCell: 083 501 0139